      <title><![CDATA[brief introduction of md grammer]]></title>
      <url>/2020/02/17/brief-introduction-of-md-grammer/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">markdown</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">main content: markdown gramer points to help you in writing beautiful md documents</span><br><span class="line">pay attention: only tested or checked right under os ubuntu and software Typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><a href="自动生成目录">toc</a></p>
<h1 id="enhance"><a href="#enhance" class="headerlink" title="enhance"></a>enhance</h1><ol>
<li>``` markdown<ul>
<li>** ***: 包围内容分别斜体，粗体，粗斜体<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   eg: *斜体*, **粗体**, ***粗斜体***</span><br><span class="line">2. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   ~~words~~ &lt;u&gt;words&lt;&#x2F;u&gt;: 包围分别为删除线与下划线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
eg: <del>删除线</del>, <u>下划线</u></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>``` markdown<br>~ ^: 包围内容分别为下标与上标，如：H<del>2</del>0, X^3^<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   eg: H~2~0, X^3^</span><br><span class="line">4. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   :emoji name: 显示emoji图像，如:happy:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
eg: :happy: :smile:</li>
<li>``` markdown<br>==: 包围内容高亮<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   eg: &#x3D;&#x3D;高亮&#x3D;&#x3D;</span><br><span class="line">6. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   &#96;: 包围显示效果如下,可用于在文字中显示函数调用等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
eg: <code>printf()</code></li>
<li><pre><code class="markdown"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">"字体名"</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">12</span>&gt;</span></span>words<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>
<span class="xml"><span class="comment"><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   eg: &lt;font color&#x3D;#0099ff size&#x3D;3 face&#x3D;&quot;黑体&quot;&gt;黑体&lt;&#x2F;font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">8. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   [^脚注名]: 需要使用&#39;[^脚注名]: 脚注内容&#39;指明脚注对应内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></span></span>
eg:  md[^markdown]
</code></pre>
</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="label"><a href="#label" class="headerlink" title="label"></a>label</h1><ol>
<li>``` markdown<br>***/+++/—: 生成水平线<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">2. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   &gt;: 引用标示，可多个连用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
<li><code>markdown
​</code>: 代码块标示，后续可制定代码语言类型（有美化效果）<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">4. &#96;&#96;&#96;markdown</span><br><span class="line">   ---: 在文档最开始使用，显示一个记录文字元信息的区块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
<li><pre><code class="markdown"></code></pre>
</li>
</ol>
   <div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">6. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   [link name](link addr &quot;title&quot;): 插入连接，鼠标悬浮显示title内容，点击跳转link addr. 可用[link name][link]+[link]: link addr &quot;title&quot;显示同样效果，此外link addr可以是页面内的锚点[link](#anchor name &quot;title&quot;)，其中锚点anchor name可以是标题锚点或者制定&lt;span&gt;标签的id</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<ol start="7">
<li>``` markdown<link addr>: 使用该方式使得点击文字有跳到链接位置效果
<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">8. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">   ![img](path name &quot;title&quot;): 与上方链接类似</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
<li>``` markdown<ol>
<li><ul>
<li><ul>
<li>or -: 前者为有序列表，后三个均为无序列表<div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">10. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">    - [ ]  - [x]: 显示单选框</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>``` markdown<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">column 1</th>
<th align="center">column 2</th>
<th align="right">column 3</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">c1_value</td>
<td align="center">c2_value</td>
<td align="right">c3_value</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left"><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">12. &#96;&#96;&#96; markdown</span><br><span class="line">    #: 标题，可多个，分别代表h1, h2, h3等等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></td>
<td align="center"></td>
<td align="right"></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      
